snippet.title: Amiga Longplay Astro Marine Corps (AMC)
snippet.description:
http://www.recordedamigagames.org

Played By: Lemm

In the days I was addicted by the music. Also it was very fun to play.

I mixed the music after playing the game in "sound FX mode" into the movie. Hope you like it.

But now, it's time to blast some Aliens ... :-) -
